  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360780/extras/3ada481e31f18db3755885da576ea3ab.avif?t=1687594694\" width=620 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CARTOON GAME</h2><br>Playing in Early Access, follow the levels, which are progressively more difficult and sophisticated. Go through all the levels.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Can you overcome it?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Ball control<br></li><li> Avoid moving obstacles<br></li><li> Run from enemies<br></li><li> Do not fall into the water<br></li><li> Balance in heights<br></li><li> Reach the finish line</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What awaits you?</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360780/extras/ae69cdfb22563a0db3b3390650dfa52b.avif?t=1687594694\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360780/extras/8ad80279919eb1c3948303bd854eeb0f.avif?t=1687594694\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360780/extras/374a7e8dbd55db63f240570904b4fbf6.avif?t=1687594694\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360780/extras/944233e0216c38d010fe941bed32a3b5.avif?t=1687594694\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360780/extras/92cc2189a89dcbac58da76497f5006e4.avif?t=1687594694\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360780/extras/7ededfce9f6492b4a8a4ee5833b27196.avif?t=1687594694\" width=620 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mystical atmosphere and obstacles</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360780/extras/89b7916629f2a2f7325b033dea05b43d.avif?t=1687594694\" width=620 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Try how handy you are and you can go through all the obstacles with the ball.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360780/extras/c70513c313a00554acfc43ff41eed1f5.avif?t=1687594694\" width=620 height=100 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360780/extras/3ada481e31f18db3755885da576ea3ab.avif?t=1687594694\" width=620 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CARTOON GAME</h2><br>Playing in Early Access, follow the levels, which are progressively more difficult and sophisticated. Go through all the levels.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Can you overcome it?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Ball control<br></li><li> Avoid moving obstacles<br></li><li> Run from enemies<br></li><li> Do not fall into the water<br></li><li> Balance in heights<br></li><li> Reach the finish line</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What awaits you?</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360780/extras/ae69cdfb22563a0db3b3390650dfa52b.avif?t=1687594694\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360780/extras/8ad80279919eb1c3948303bd854eeb0f.avif?t=1687594694\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360780/extras/374a7e8dbd55db63f240570904b4fbf6.avif?t=1687594694\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360780/extras/944233e0216c38d010fe941bed32a3b5.avif?t=1687594694\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360780/extras/92cc2189a89dcbac58da76497f5006e4.avif?t=1687594694\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360780/extras/7eded